<font color="#ffff00">2,500.</font>

843
01:29:11,120 --> 01:29:14,840
<font color="#ffffff">MURMURS FROM BUYERS</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I have...</font>

844
01:29:14,840 --> 01:29:17,240
<font color="#ffffff">What was it?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">1,200.</font>

845
01:29:17,240 --> 01:29:19,680
<font color="#ffffff">I have 1,200, once...</font>

846
01:29:19,680 --> 01:29:22,560
<font color="#ffffff">Twice... </font><font color="#ffff00">3,000!</font>

847
01:29:22,560 --> 01:29:25,200
<font color="#ffffff">Sold for 1,200!</font>

848
01:29:25,200 --> 01:29:29,280
<font color="#ffff00">That's unfair! I...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You'd better leave, sir.</font>

849
01:29:29,280 --> 01:29:31,400
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, no, you...</font>

850
01:29:33,960 --> 01:29:36,360
<font color="#ffffff">GASPS OF HORROR</font>

851
01:29:45,240 --> 01:29:48,120
<font color="#ffff00">What took you so long? </font><font color="#ffffff">Let's go.</font>

852
01:29:48,120 --> 01:29:52,680
<font color="#ffff00">Wait! I haven't finished bidding.</font>
