853
01:29:52,680 --> 01:29:55,200
<font color="#ffff00">Too bad, old man. Keep trying.</font>

854
01:29:56,160 --> 01:29:58,360
<font color="#ffff00">Not so rough!</font>

855
01:30:05,520 --> 01:30:10,320
<font color="#ffff00">Handle with care, fellows.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm valuable property.</font>

856
01:30:12,760 --> 01:30:17,720
<font color="#ffff00">I want to thank you gentlemen</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for saving my life. Thank you.</font>

857
01:30:17,720 --> 01:30:20,760
<font color="#ffffff">Save it for the Station House.</font>

858
01:30:24,080 --> 01:30:29,320
<font color="#ffff00">Let's have some good cheer. You're</font>
