<font color="#ffffff">We'll find out when we book you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for being drunk and disorderly.</font>

860
01:30:34,680 --> 01:30:38,760
<font color="#ffff00">That's chicken feed.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">You've hit the jackpot.</font>

861
01:30:38,760 --> 01:30:44,720
<font color="#ffff00">"Chicago Police capture</font>
<font color="#ffff00">United Nations Killer."</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm Roger Thornhill.</font>

862
01:30:47,840 --> 01:30:49,680
<font color="#ffffff">It's HIM.</font>

863
01:30:49,680 --> 01:30:52,200
<font color="#ffff00">Congratulations, men.</font>

864
01:30:52,200 --> 01:30:56,680
<font color="#ffffff">Yeah...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">This is 1055. ></font>

865
01:30:56,680 --> 01:30:59,880
<font color="#ffffff">We have a man here, Thornhill.</font>

866
01:30:59,880 --> 01:31:03,560
<font color="#ffffff">Code 76. Wanted by NYPD. ></font>

867
01:31:03,560 --> 01:31:06,560
<font color="#ffffff">Positive ID. ></font>

868
01:31:06,560 --> 01:31:08,680
<font color="#ffffff">Absolutely.</font>

869
01:31:08,680 --> 01:31:13,480
<font color="#ffffff">Michigan Ave, proceeding north</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to 42nd Precinct. ></font>

870
01:31:15,520 --> 01:31:17,600
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font>

871
01:31:17,600 --> 01:31:20,360
<font color="#ffffff">Come again.</font>

872
01:31:22,800 --> 01:31:24,960
<font color="#ffffff">Are you sure?</font>

873
01:31:24,960 --> 01:31:28,480
<font color="#ffffff">OK. Right. Yeah, I've got it.</font>

874
01:31:28,480 --> 01:31:31,080
<font color="#ffffff">1055, off and clear.</font>

875
01:31:31,080 --> 01:31:34,840
<font color="#ffffff">Where are we going?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Airport.</font>

876
01:31:34,840 --> 01:31:37,800
<font color="#ffffff">For what?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Orders!</font>

877
01:31:37,800 --> 01:31:42,760
<font color="#ffff00">The airport! I want to be taken</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Police Headquarters.</font>

878
01:31:42,760 --> 01:31:48,440
<font color="#ffff00">Why do you think I sent for you?</font>
