879
01:31:48,440 --> 01:31:53,000
<font color="#ffffff">Sit back. </font><font color="#ffff00">I want to go</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Police Headquarters.</font>

880
01:31:53,000 --> 01:31:58,080
<font color="#ffff00">I'm a mad killer on the loose!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You should be ashamed of yourself.</font>

881
01:32:13,600 --> 01:32:18,600
<font color="#ffffff">TANNOY:</font>
<font color="#ffffff">'Announcing Flight 29,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">arriving at Gate 12.'</font>

882
01:32:22,400 --> 01:32:25,000
<font color="#ffffff">He said right here.</font>

883
01:32:25,000 --> 01:32:27,520
<font color="#ffff00">Does anyone mind if I sit down?</font>

884
01:32:27,520 --> 01:32:33,680
<font color="#ffffff">TANNOY:</font>
<font color="#ffffff">'Final call, American Airlines</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Flight 48.</font>

885
01:32:33,680 --> 01:32:37,400
<font color="#ffffff">'Now boarding at gate no 14.'</font>

886
01:32:37,400 --> 01:32:41,280
<font color="#00ffff">Ah! I thought I'd never make it.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Getting old.</font>

887
01:32:41,280 --> 01:32:43,200
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you.</font>

888
01:32:43,200 --> 01:32:48,600
<font color="#00ffff">This way, Mr Thornhill. </font><font color="#ffff00">Wait...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We haven't much time. This way.</font>

889
01:32:51,520 --> 01:32:54,120
<font color="#ffff00">I don't think I caught your name.</font>

890
01:32:54,120 --> 01:32:56,520
<font color="#00ffff">I don't think I pitched it.</font>

891
01:32:56,520 --> 01:32:59,440
<font color="#ffff00">You're police, or is it FBI?</font>

892
01:32:59,440 --> 01:33:04,360
<font color="#00ffff">FBI, CIA, ONI, we're all in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the same alphabet soup.</font>

893
01:33:04,360 --> 01:33:09,920
<font color="#ffff00">I had nothing to do with that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">United Nations killing. </font><font color="#00ffff">We know.</font>

894
01:33:09,920 --> 01:33:17,120
<font color="#ffff00">Then why did you let the police</font>
<font color="#ffff00">chase me? </font><font color="#00ffff">We try not to interfere</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the police.</font>

895
01:33:17,120 --> 01:33:22,000
<font color="#00ffff">Now it's become necessary. </font><font color="#ffff00">Ah.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I take it I will be cleared?</font>

896
01:33:22,000 --> 01:33:27,080
<font color="#00ffff">Do walk faster, or we'll miss</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the plane. </font><font color="#ffff00">Where are we going?</font>

897
01:33:27,080 --> 01:33:30,480
<font color="#00ffff">Rapid City, South Dakota.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What for!?</font>

898
01:33:30,480 --> 01:33:37,720
<font color="#00ffff">It's near Mount Rushmore.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I've SEEN Mount Rushmore.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">So is your friend Mr Vandamm.</font>

899
01:33:37,720 --> 01:33:40,080
<font color="#ffff00">Vandamm?!</font>

900
01:33:40,080 --> 01:33:45,240
<font color="#00ffff">Rather a formidable gentleman, eh?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">And that little tramp with him?</font>

901
01:33:45,240 --> 01:33:50,040
<font color="#00ffff">Miss Kendall? His mistress.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What's Vandamm up to?</font>

902
01:33:50,040 --> 01:33:55,480
<font color="#00ffff">You could say he's an importer/</font>
<font color="#00ffff">exporter. </font><font color="#ffff00">Of what?</font>

903
01:33:55,480 --> 01:33:58,400
<font color="#00ffff">Oh...government secrets, perhaps.</font>

904
01:33:58,400 --> 01:34:04,480
<font color="#ffff00">Why don't you grab him? </font><font color="#00ffff">We want to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">know more about his organisation.</font>

905
01:34:04,480 --> 01:34:12,320
<font color="#ffff00">What's this to do with Mt Rushmore?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Vandamm is there. We think he's</font>
<font color="#00ffff">leaving the country tomorrow night.</font>

906
01:34:12,320 --> 01:34:16,960
<font color="#ffff00">You going to stop him? </font><font color="#00ffff">No.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Why are we going?</font>

907
01:34:16,960 --> 01:34:23,120
<font color="#00ffff">To set his mind at ease</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about Kaplain. </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh, you!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">YOU're George Kaplain.</font>

908
01:34:23,120 --> 01:34:26,640
<font color="#00ffff">There is NO such person as Kaplain.</font>

909
01:34:26,640 --> 01:34:31,920
<font color="#ffff00">What do you mean? I've been</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in his hotel, tried his clothes.</font>

910
01:34:31,920 --> 01:34:34,080
<font color="#00ffff">He doesn't exist.</font>

911
01:34:34,080 --> 01:34:40,480
<font color="#00ffff">Which is why I want you to go on</font>
<font color="#00ffff">being him for the next 24 hours.</font>

912
01:34:40,480 --> 01:34:42,920
<font color="#00ffff">We'll discuss it on the plane.</font>

913
01:34:42,920 --> 01:34:49,520
<font color="#ffffff">PLANE ENGINE DROWNS OUT VOICES</font>

914
01:35:02,920 --> 01:35:08,120
<font color="#ffff00">..You started the decoy business</font>
<font color="#ffff00">without me, YOU finish it.</font>

915
01:35:08,120 --> 01:35:12,960
<font color="#00ffff">Well, we might have... </font><font color="#ffff00">You ought</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to give me a medal</font>

916
01:35:12,960 --> 01:35:18,040
<font color="#ffff00">instead of asking me to be a target</font>
<font color="#ffff00">so your agent doesn't get shot at!</font>

917
01:35:18,040 --> 01:35:23,080
<font color="#00ffff">Not shot at, found out. Once</font>
<font color="#00ffff">found out, they're as good as dead.</font>

918
01:35:23,080 --> 01:35:27,680
<font color="#00ffff">Thanks to you, suspicion is already</font>
<font color="#00ffff">forming. </font><font color="#ffff00">Thanks to me?</font>

919
01:35:27,680 --> 01:35:32,000
<font color="#ffff00">I'm an advertising man,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">NOT a red herring.</font>

920
01:35:32,000 --> 01:35:37,040
<font color="#ffff00">I've got a secretary, a mother</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and two ex-wives dependent upon me.</font>

921
01:35:37,040 --> 01:35:39,960
<font color="#ffff00">I can't afford</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to be slightly killed.</font>

922
01:35:39,960 --> 01:35:42,240
<font color="#ffff00">The answer is no.</font>

923
01:35:42,240 --> 01:35:44,800
<font color="#00ffff">Is that final? </font><font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

924
01:35:44,800 --> 01:35:50,360
<font color="#00ffff">Goodbye. </font><font color="#ffff00">Goodbye. </font><font color="#00ffff">Then there's</font>
<font color="#00ffff">no need to talk about Miss Kendall,</font>

925
01:35:50,360 --> 01:35:56,720
<font color="#00ffff">of whom you obviously disapprove?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">You're using sex like a fly-swatter.</font>

926
01:35:56,720 --> 01:36:04,040
<font color="#00ffff">I don't suppose it matters to you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that she was forced to do</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what she did to protect herself.</font>

927
01:36:04,040 --> 01:36:08,280
<font color="#ffff00">From what? </font><font color="#00ffff">Exposure.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Assassination.</font>

928
01:36:08,280 --> 01:36:11,480
<font color="#00ffff">You see, Mr Thornhill, she...</font>

929
01:36:11,480 --> 01:36:14,160
<font color="#00ffff">she's one of our agents.</font>

930
01:36:14,160 --> 01:36:16,280
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, no...</font>

931
01:36:16,280 --> 01:36:21,520
<font color="#00ffff">I'm afraid you HAVE put her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in a very dangerous situation.</font>

932
01:36:21,520 --> 01:36:25,600
<font color="#00ffff">And much more than her life</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is at stake.</font>

933
01:36:37,600 --> 01:36:40,560
<font color="#ffff00">Suppose they don't come?</font>

934
01:36:40,560 --> 01:36:42,760
<font color="#00ffff">They'll come.</font>

935
01:36:42,760 --> 01:36:47,640
<font color="#ffff00">I don't like the way</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Teddy Roosevelt is looking at me.</font>

936
01:36:47,640 --> 01:36:53,280
<font color="#00ffff">He's giving you a word of caution:</font>
<font color="#00ffff">"Speak softly, carry a big stick."</font>

937
01:36:53,280 --> 01:36:56,760
<font color="#ffff00">Or NOT to go through</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with this scheme.</font>

938
01:36:56,760 --> 01:37:03,080
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps he doesn't know that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you caused our problem.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I don't accept that.</font>

939
01:37:03,080 --> 01:37:09,520
<font color="#00ffff">If you hadn't been so attractive</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to Miss Kendall... </font><font color="#ffff00">And vice-versa.</font>

940
01:37:09,520 --> 01:37:16,520
<font color="#00ffff">..Vandamm wouldn't be suspicious.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">It's clear she is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">emotionally involved.</font>

941
01:37:16,520 --> 01:37:23,320
<font color="#00ffff">AND with a man who's a government</font>
<font color="#00ffff">agent. </font><font color="#ffff00">Are you saying I am</font>
<font color="#ffff00">irresistible?</font>

942
01:37:23,320 --> 01:37:28,400
<font color="#00ffff">I'm trying to remind you that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">YOU have a responsibility to help</font>

943
01:37:28,400 --> 01:37:30,800
<font color="#00ffff">up until he leaves the country.</font>

944
01:37:30,800 --> 01:37:32,800
<font color="#ffff00">All right.</font>

945
01:37:32,800 --> 01:37:38,280
<font color="#ffff00">And AFTER tonight?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">My blessings on you both.</font>

946
01:37:51,640 --> 01:37:54,280
<font color="#ffff00">Here they are.</font>

947
01:38:43,600 --> 01:38:46,200
<font color="#00ff00">Good afternoon, Mr Kaplain.</font>

948
01:38:46,200 --> 01:38:48,280
<font color="#ffff00">Not her.</font>

949
01:38:55,320 --> 01:39:00,680
<font color="#00ff00">Did I misunderstand you about</font>
<font color="#00ff00">bringing her here? </font><font color="#ffff00">No, you didn't.</font>

950
01:39:00,680 --> 01:39:07,280
<font color="#ffff00">I suppose my call surprised you?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">No. I knew the police</font>
<font color="#00ff00">would release you.</font>

951
01:39:07,280 --> 01:39:14,400
<font color="#00ff00">By the way, my compliments</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on your colourful exit</font>
<font color="#00ff00">from the auction. </font><font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

952
01:39:14,400 --> 01:39:18,200
<font color="#00ff00">Now what little drama</font>
<font color="#00ff00">are we here for?</font>

953
01:39:18,200 --> 01:39:25,400
<font color="#00ff00">I don't believe you've invited me</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to these gay surroundings to come</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to a business arrangement.</font>

954
01:39:25,400 --> 01:39:33,280
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I not only know WHEN</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you are leaving the country,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but your ultimate destination.</font>

955
01:39:33,280 --> 01:39:37,040
<font color="#00ff00">You wouldn't care to carry</font>
<font color="#00ff00">my bags(!)</font>

956
01:39:37,040 --> 01:39:44,400
<font color="#ffff00">I would be interested in the price</font>
<font color="#ffff00">just the same. </font><font color="#00ff00">The price?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">For doing nothing to stop you.</font>

957
01:39:44,400 --> 01:39:48,120
<font color="#00ff00">How much did you have in mind?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">The girl.</font>

958
01:39:48,120 --> 01:39:53,080
<font color="#ffff00">I want the girl to get</font>
<font color="#ffff00">what's coming to her.</font>

959
01:39:53,080 --> 01:39:57,440
<font color="#ffff00">I'll see there's enough</font>
<font color="#ffff00">pinned on her</font>

960
01:39:57,440 --> 01:40:03,680
<font color="#ffff00">to make her life uncomfortable.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Do that and I'll let you go.</font>

961
01:40:03,680 --> 01:40:06,160
<font color="#00ff00">She really did get under your skin.</font>

962
01:40:06,160 --> 01:40:11,320
<font color="#ffff00">We're talking about YOUR skin. I'm</font>
<font color="#ffff00">offering you a chance to save it.</font>

963
01:40:11,320 --> 01:40:14,960
<font color="#00ff00">To EXCHANGE it.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Put it any way you like.</font>

964
01:40:14,960 --> 01:40:17,760
<font color="#00ff00">I'm curious, Mr Kaplain.</font>

965
01:40:17,760 --> 01:40:25,120
<font color="#00ff00">How did you reach the deduction</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that my feelings for Miss Kendall</font>
<font color="#00ff00">had deteriorated to SUCH an extent?</font>

966
01:40:25,120 --> 01:40:28,160
<font color="#ffff00">I don't deduce, I observe.</font>

967
01:40:30,800 --> 01:40:35,720
<font color="#ffffff">Philip, if you don't mind,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm going back to the house.</font>

968
01:40:46,520 --> 01:40:49,400
<font color="#ffff00">Just a second, you. </font><font color="#ffffff">Stay away!</font>

969
01:40:49,400 --> 01:40:51,640
<font color="#ffffff">< Let go of me.</font>

970
01:40:51,640 --> 01:40:54,240
<font color="#ffffff">Stay away from me. Let go!</font>

971
01:40:54,240 --> 01:40:57,480
<font color="#ffffff">Let go of me! </font><font color="#ffff00">Save the phoney tears.</font>

972
01:41:00,160 --> 01:41:04,160
<font color="#ffff00">You little fool!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Just stay away from me.</font>

973
01:41:09,160 --> 01:41:11,400
<font color="#00ffff">(Let her go.)</font>

974
01:41:13,720 --> 01:41:16,160
<font color="#00ffff">Don't touch anything.</font>

975
01:42:08,000 --> 01:42:09,920
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Thornhill.</font>

976
01:42:17,200 --> 01:42:19,760
<font color="#00ffff">Don't be long.</font>

977
01:42:21,680 --> 01:42:23,840
<font color="#ffffff">Hello.</font>

978
01:42:23,840 --> 01:42:25,840
<font color="#ffff00">Hello.</font>

979
01:42:25,840 --> 01:42:29,720
<font color="#ffffff">Are you all right?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, I think so.</font>

980
01:42:29,720 --> 01:42:33,760
<font color="#ffffff">I asked the Professor</font>
<font color="#ffffff">if I could see you.</font>

981
01:42:33,760 --> 01:42:36,040
<font color="#ffff00">Oh?</font>

982
01:42:36,040 --> 01:42:38,600
<font color="#ffffff">There's not much time.</font>

983
01:42:38,600 --> 01:42:41,120
<font color="#ffff00">Isn't there?</font>

984
01:42:41,120 --> 01:42:44,760
<font color="#ffffff">I wanted to tell...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I mean, apologise...</font>

985
01:42:45,800 --> 01:42:47,840
<font color="#ffff00">No need.</font>

986
01:42:47,840 --> 01:42:51,040
<font color="#ffff00">I understand.</font>

987
01:42:51,040 --> 01:42:53,840
<font color="#ffff00">All in the line of duty.</font>

988
01:42:55,080 --> 01:43:00,440
<font color="#ffffff">I DID treat you miserably.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I hated you for it.</font>

989
01:43:00,440 --> 01:43:04,440
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't want you to go on</font>
<font color="#ffffff">thinking that...</font>

990
01:43:05,440 --> 01:43:09,600
<font color="#ffff00">I-I used some pretty harsh words.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry.</font>

991
01:43:09,600 --> 01:43:12,400
<font color="#ffffff">They hurt deeply. </font><font color="#ffff00">If I'd known...</font>

992
01:43:12,400 --> 01:43:16,800
<font color="#ffffff">I couldn't tell you. </font><font color="#ffff00">Of course not.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Could I?</font>

993
01:43:16,800 --> 01:43:19,640
<font color="#ffff00">No, I guess not.</font>

994
01:43:19,640 --> 01:43:23,800
<font color="#ffffff">You didn't get hurt.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm SO relieved.</font>

995
01:43:23,800 --> 01:43:30,840
<font color="#ffff00">Of course I was hurt! </font><font color="#ffffff">I mean</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in the cafeteria when I shot you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with the blanks. </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh, THAT.</font>

996
01:43:30,840 --> 01:43:35,800
<font color="#ffffff">You did it rather well. </font><font color="#ffff00">Yes,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I thought I was quite graceful.</font>

997
01:43:35,800 --> 01:43:38,880
<font color="#ffffff">Considering it's not really</font>
<font color="#ffffff">your kind of work.</font>

998
01:43:38,880 --> 01:43:44,000
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I got into it by accident.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What's YOUR excuse?</font>

999
01:43:44,000 --> 01:43:49,000
<font color="#ffffff">I met Philip Vandamm at a party</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and saw only his charm.</font>

1000
01:43:49,000 --> 01:43:51,200
<font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font>

1001
01:43:51,200 --> 01:43:56,680
<font color="#ffffff">I had nothing to do that weekend,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">so I decided to fall in love.</font>

1002
01:43:58,000 --> 01:44:00,760
<font color="#ffff00">That's nice.</font>

1003
01:44:00,760 --> 01:44:08,360
<font color="#ffffff">Eventually, the Professor and</font>
<font color="#ffffff">his colleagues approached me with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">some sordid details about Philip.</font>

1004
01:44:08,360 --> 01:44:14,520
<font color="#ffffff">They told me that my relationship</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with him made me uniquely valuable</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to them.</font>

1005
01:44:14,520 --> 01:44:17,440
<font color="#ffff00">So, you became a Girl Scout?</font>

1006
01:44:17,440 --> 01:44:22,520
<font color="#ffffff">Maybe it was the first time anyone</font>
<font color="#ffffff">asked me to do anything worthwhile.</font>

1007
01:44:22,520 --> 01:44:27,840
<font color="#ffff00">Has life been like THAT?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mm-hm.</font>

1008
01:44:27,840 --> 01:44:29,960
<font color="#ffff00">How come?</font>

1009
01:44:31,920 --> 01:44:34,400
<font color="#ffffff">..Men like you.</font>

1010
01:44:34,400 --> 01:44:37,360
<font color="#ffff00">What's wrong with men like me?</font>

1011
01:44:37,360 --> 01:44:39,880
<font color="#ffffff">They don't believe in marriage.</font>

1012
01:44:39,880 --> 01:44:44,120
<font color="#ffff00">I've been married twice.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">See what I mean?</font>

1013
01:44:44,120 --> 01:44:48,160
<font color="#ffff00">I may go back to hating you.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It was more fun.</font>

1014
01:44:54,000 --> 01:44:56,040
<font color="#ffffff">Goodbye, darling.</font>

1015
01:44:56,040 --> 01:44:58,680
<font color="#ffff00">Wait a minute. Not so soon.</font>

1016
01:44:58,680 --> 01:45:02,800
<font color="#ffffff">I have to go and convince them</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I took the long way round.</font>

1017
01:45:02,800 --> 01:45:07,000
<font color="#ffff00">Couldn't we stand like this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for just a few hours?</font>

1018
01:45:07,000 --> 01:45:13,920
<font color="#ffffff">You're supposed to be dying.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I've never felt more alive.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Whose side are you on?</font>

1019
01:45:13,920 --> 01:45:16,200
<font color="#ffff00">Yours always.</font>

1020
01:45:16,200 --> 01:45:20,720
<font color="#ffffff">Please don't undermine my resolve</font>
<font color="#ffffff">when I need it most.</font>

1021
01:45:20,720 --> 01:45:22,960
<font color="#ffffff">< CAR HORN</font>

1022
01:45:27,920 --> 01:45:33,960
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, well, I guess it's off</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to hospital for me and back</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to danger for you.</font>

1023
01:45:33,960 --> 01:45:38,680
<font color="#ffffff">It's much safer now, thanks to you,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">my darling decoy.</font>

1024
01:45:38,680 --> 01:45:42,840
<font color="#ffff00">Don't thank me. I can't stand</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it. </font><font color="#ffffff">All right, I won't.</font>

1025
01:45:42,840 --> 01:45:49,680
<font color="#ffff00">After your friend Vandamm</font>
<font color="#ffff00">takes off, you and I will get</font>
<font color="#ffff00">together in private.</font>

1026
01:45:49,680 --> 01:45:52,760
<font color="#ffffff">You know that can't be. </font><font color="#ffff00">It CAN be.</font>

1027
01:45:55,200 --> 01:45:57,880
<font color="#ffffff">Well, he HAS told you, hasn't he?</font>

1028
01:45:57,880 --> 01:46:00,320
<font color="#ffff00">Told me WHAT?</font>

1029
01:46:00,320 --> 01:46:02,760
<font color="#00ffff">We better get moving.</font>

1030
01:46:02,760 --> 01:46:05,040
<font color="#ffff00">What didn't you tell me? </font><font color="#ffffff">Professor?</font>

1031
01:46:05,040 --> 01:46:12,080
<font color="#00ffff">She's going off with Vandamm</font>
<font color="#00ffff">tonight on the plane.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">She's going off with Vandamm?</font>

1032
01:46:12,080 --> 01:46:15,160
<font color="#00ffff">That's why we set up the charade.</font>

1033
01:46:15,160 --> 01:46:18,720
<font color="#00ffff">So that Vandamm HAD to take her.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">But...</font>

1034
01:46:18,720 --> 01:46:23,920
<font color="#00ffff">She can be valuable to us</font>
<font color="#00ffff">over there. </font><font color="#ffff00">You lied to me!</font>

1035
01:46:23,920 --> 01:46:26,200
<font color="#00ffff">I needed your help.</font>

1036
01:46:26,200 --> 01:46:31,000
<font color="#ffffff">Don't be angry. </font><font color="#ffff00">You can't do it.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">She HAS to!</font>

1037
01:46:31,000 --> 01:46:35,120
<font color="#ffff00">Nobody HAS to do anything.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I don't like these games.</font>

1038
01:46:35,120 --> 01:46:38,880
<font color="#00ffff">War is hell, even a cold one.</font>

1039
01:46:38,880 --> 01:46:45,240
<font color="#ffff00">If you can't lick the Vandamms</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of this world without using</font>
<font color="#ffff00">girls like her,</font>

1040
01:46:45,240 --> 01:46:49,680
<font color="#ffff00">perhaps you need to LOSE</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a few cold wars!</font>

1041
01:46:49,680 --> 01:46:53,040
<font color="#00ffff">I'm afraid we're already</font>
<font color="#00ffff">doing that.</font>

1042
01:46:58,800 --> 01:47:02,840
<font color="#ffff00">I won't let you go.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Don't spoil everything.</font>

1043
01:47:07,640 --> 01:47:15,480
<font color="#ffffff">RADIO:</font>
<font color="#ffffff">'..shot Mr Kaplain twice in front of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">scores of horrified men, women</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and children.</font>

1044
01:47:15,480 --> 01:47:21,880
<font color="#ffffff">'Witnesses described the women</font>
<font color="#ffffff">as an attractive blonde</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in her late twenties.</font>

1045
01:47:21,880 --> 01:47:26,920
<font color="#ffffff">'Kaplain was rushed to hospital</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in a critical condition.</font>

1046
01:47:26,920 --> 01:47:32,920
<font color="#ffffff">'Kaplain was tentatively identified</font>
<font color="#ffffff">as an employee of the Federal</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Government.</font>

1047
01:47:32,920 --> 01:47:36,760
<font color="#ffffff">'A bus-boy in the Mount Rushmore</font>
<font color="#ffffff">cafeteria...'</font>

1048
01:47:36,760 --> 01:47:39,040
<font color="#ffffff">< KEY IN DOOR</font>

1049
01:47:42,600 --> 01:47:45,280
<font color="#00ffff">Here we are. </font><font color="#ffff00">Hello.</font>

1050
01:47:45,280 --> 01:47:48,920
<font color="#00ffff">Slacks, shirt, and these.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

1051
01:47:48,920 --> 01:47:56,080
<font color="#00ffff">They'll do for you around here</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for the next couple of days.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Couple of days?</font>

1052
01:47:56,080 --> 01:47:58,480
<font color="#00ffff">Hey! </font><font color="#ffff00">What? </font><font color="#00ffff">What's this?</font>

1053
01:47:58,480 --> 01:48:03,520
<font color="#ffff00">That's where I hit the chair</font>
<font color="#ffff00">during that phoney fall.</font>

1054
01:48:03,520 --> 01:48:11,360
<font color="#00ffff">Otherwise feeling all right?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Fine. Considering your driver</font>
<font color="#ffff00">has a sledge-hammer for a hand.</font>

1055
01:48:11,360 --> 01:48:17,360
<font color="#00ffff">Sorry. </font><font color="#ffff00">I deserved it. I guess</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I deserve that locked door, too.</font>

1056
01:48:17,360 --> 01:48:22,040
<font color="#00ffff">If you were seen it could prove</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fatal for Miss Kendall.</font>

1057
01:48:22,040 --> 01:48:25,800
<font color="#ffff00">I've begun to forget her already.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Good.</font>

1058
01:48:25,800 --> 01:48:31,400
<font color="#00ffff">Better that way.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Inside of an hour, she'll be gone.</font>

1059
01:48:31,400 --> 01:48:35,280
<font color="#ffff00">Oh. How's everything</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in Rapid City?</font>

1060
01:48:35,280 --> 01:48:41,240
<font color="#00ffff">Fine. Mr Kaplain's shooting</font>
<font color="#00ffff">has acquired the authority</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of the printed word.</font>

1061
01:48:41,240 --> 01:48:45,400
<font color="#00ffff">Everyone's been co-operating well.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Including me.</font>

1062
01:48:45,400 --> 01:48:48,200
<font color="#ffff00">I'm co-operative. </font><font color="#00ffff">I'm grateful.</font>

1063
01:48:48,200 --> 01:48:51,800
<font color="#ffff00">Care to do me a favour? </font><font color="#00ffff">Anything.</font>

1064
01:48:51,800 --> 01:48:56,840
<font color="#ffff00">I'd like a drink. Can you get me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">some bourbon? A pint will do.</font>

1065
01:48:56,840 --> 01:49:03,720
<font color="#00ffff">Can I join you? </font><font color="#ffff00">If you do,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you'd better make it a quart.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">See you in a few minutes.</font>

1066
01:49:30,720 --> 01:49:32,720
<font color="#ffff00">What a m...!</font>

1067
01:50:05,240 --> 01:50:07,680
<font color="#ffffff">Stop! </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh, excuse me.</font>

1068
01:50:07,680 --> 01:50:10,200
<font color="#ffffff">Stop...</font>

1069
01:50:10,200 --> 01:50:12,600
<font color="#ffff00">Ah-ah-ah...</font>

1070
01:50:31,080 --> 01:50:36,080
<font color="#ffffff">Sure you don't want me to take you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">up there? </font><font color="#ffff00">Never mind. This is fine.</font>

1071
01:52:09,800 --> 01:52:12,760
<font color="#ffffff">CAR DRAWING UP ></font>

1072
01:53:15,760 --> 01:53:18,120
<font color="#ffffff">EVE:</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I just lost my head.</font>

1073
01:53:18,120 --> 01:53:23,560
<font color="#00ff00">I'm not trying to make you feel</font>
<font color="#00ff00">better. I mean it.</font>

1074
01:53:23,560 --> 01:53:30,040
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't mean it...</font>
<font color="#00ff00">He wanted to destroy you.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You had to protect yourself.</font>

1075
01:53:30,040 --> 01:53:34,640
<font color="#00ff00">Soon we will be off and I shall</font>
<font color="#00ff00">dedicate myself to you.</font>

1076
01:53:34,640 --> 01:53:37,800
<font color="#00ff00">What's the situation, Leonard?</font>

1077
01:53:37,800 --> 01:53:42,760
<font color="#00ffff">About the plane, you mean?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Yes. What's the latest report?</font>

1078
01:53:42,760 --> 01:53:45,080
<font color="#00ffff">On course, 6,000 and descending.</font>

1079
01:53:45,080 --> 01:53:47,880
<font color="#00ff00">We've got ten minutes. </font><font color="#00ffff">At the most.</font>

1080
01:53:47,880 --> 01:53:55,080
<font color="#00ffff">And... I wonder if I may have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a few moments of parting</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with you, sir. </font><font color="#00ff00">Certainly.</font>

1081
01:53:55,080 --> 01:53:58,240
<font color="#00ffff">In private? </font><font color="#ffffff">I'll get my things.</font>

1082
01:53:58,240 --> 01:54:03,080
<font color="#00ff00">Well, Leonard,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">how does one say goodbye</font>

1083
01:54:03,080 --> 01:54:05,480
<font color="#00ff00">to one's right arm?</font>

1084
01:54:10,960 --> 01:54:13,680
<font color="#00ffff">You may wish you had cut it off.</font>

1085
01:54:15,080 --> 01:54:16,640
<font color="#00ff00">Mmm?</font>

1086
01:54:16,640 --> 01:54:20,440
<font color="#00ffff">I know how fond you are</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Miss Kendall,</font>

1087
01:54:20,440 --> 01:54:23,040
<font color="#00ffff">and I find this a terrible thing...</font>

1088
01:54:27,080 --> 01:54:29,960
<font color="#00ffff">She's not to be trusted...</font>

1089
01:54:36,440 --> 01:54:40,680
<font color="#ffffff">COIN CLATTERS ON GROUND</font>

1090
01:54:44,920 --> 01:54:48,040
<font color="#ffffff">COIN HITS GLASS</font>

1091
01:55:03,440 --> 01:55:06,160
<font color="#00ffff">It couldn't have been anything.</font>

1092
01:55:09,040 --> 01:55:13,680
<font color="#00ffff">YOU must have had doubts about her.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">And still do.</font>

1093
01:55:13,680 --> 01:55:18,400
<font color="#00ff00">Rubbish. </font><font color="#00ffff">Why else</font>
<font color="#00ffff">didn't you tell her</font>

1094
01:55:18,400 --> 01:55:21,120
<font color="#00ffff">that the microfilm is hidden here?</font>

1095
01:55:21,120 --> 01:55:26,480
<font color="#00ff00">You're trying to poison my mind.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">The truth... </font><font color="#00ff00">The truth?</font>

1096
01:55:26,480 --> 01:55:29,040
<font color="#00ff00">It's innuendo!</font>

1097
01:55:29,040 --> 01:55:37,200
<font color="#00ffff">Call it my "women's intuition"</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but I've never trusted neatness.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">She shot him in a moment of anger.</font>

1098
01:55:37,200 --> 01:55:40,240
<font color="#00ff00">You were there. You saw it. </font><font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

1099
01:55:42,160 --> 01:55:46,720
<font color="#00ffff">And thereby wrapped everything up</font>
<font color="#00ffff">into a neat bundle(!)</font>

1100
01:55:46,720 --> 01:55:51,840
<font color="#00ffff">A - She removed any doubts you had</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about her devotion.</font>

1101
01:55:51,840 --> 01:55:58,200
<font color="#00ffff">B - She gave herself an urgent</font>
<font color="#00ffff">reason to be taken with you.</font>

1102
01:56:00,080 --> 01:56:02,760
<font color="#00ff00">You know what I think...?</font>

1103
01:56:02,760 --> 01:56:07,320
<font color="#00ff00">I think you're jealous.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I'm VERY touched. Very...</font>

1104
01:56:08,320 --> 01:56:12,800
<font color="#00ff00">Leonard...?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">GUN FIRES</font>

1105
01:56:17,200 --> 01:56:19,760
<font color="#00ffff">The gun she shot Kaplain with.</font>

1106
01:56:19,760 --> 01:56:26,880
<font color="#00ffff">It's an old Gestapo trick -</font>
<font color="#00ffff">shoot one of your own people</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to show you're not one of them.</font>

1107
01:56:26,880 --> 01:56:30,400
<font color="#00ffff">THEY'VE just used blank cartridges.</font>

1108
01:56:39,240 --> 01:56:41,680
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS</font>

1109
01:56:43,080 --> 01:56:46,120
<font color="#ffffff">What was that noise?</font>

1110
01:56:46,120 --> 01:56:50,640
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, we wondered what it was, too.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Didn't we, Leonard?</font>

1111
01:56:50,640 --> 01:56:53,880
<font color="#00ff00">Hurry up. It's almost time to go.</font>

1112
01:56:53,880 --> 01:56:55,520
<font color="#ffffff">In a moment.</font>

1113
01:56:57,000 --> 01:57:00,040
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR CLOSES ></font>

1114
01:57:03,280 --> 01:57:07,960
<font color="#00ffff">You're not taking her with you?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Of course I am.</font>

1115
01:57:07,960 --> 01:57:13,120
<font color="#00ff00">Like our friends, I too</font>
<font color="#00ff00">believe in neatness, Leonard.</font>

1116
01:57:13,120 --> 01:57:18,040
<font color="#00ff00">This matter is best disposed of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">from a great height, over water.</font>

1117
01:58:01,120 --> 01:58:05,160
<font color="#00ff00">How about a little champagne</font>
<font color="#00ff00">before we go?</font>

1118
01:58:05,160 --> 01:58:07,920
<font color="#ffffff">I'd love it. </font><font color="#00ffff">It'll kill the time.</font>

1119
01:58:07,920 --> 01:58:11,000
<font color="#ffffff">Over the rocks would be fine.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Sure.</font>

1120
01:58:14,040 --> 01:58:17,440
<font color="#ffffff">CLINK OF GLASSES ></font>

1121
01:59:19,840 --> 01:59:23,960
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you. </font><font color="#00ff00">To YOU, my dear,</font>

1122
01:59:23,960 --> 01:59:28,200
<font color="#00ff00">and all the lovely moments</font>
<font color="#00ff00">we've had together.</font>

1123
01:59:29,880 --> 01:59:31,960
<font color="#00ffff">There he is.</font>

1124
01:59:31,960 --> 01:59:36,480
<font color="#ffffff">PLANE DRAWS CLOSER</font>

1125
01:59:39,040 --> 01:59:42,520
<font color="#00ff00">Jump in, Leonard.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">The champagne's fine.</font>

1126
01:59:42,520 --> 01:59:48,480
<font color="#00ffff">There's no time.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You always were a spoilsport.</font>

1127
01:59:51,640 --> 01:59:56,520
<font color="#00ffff">It would please me if you would</font>
<font color="#00ffff">think of me as being with you,</font>

1128
01:59:56,520 --> 01:59:59,800
<font color="#00ffff">if only in spirit. </font><font color="#ffffff">I shall.</font>

1129
02:00:07,160 --> 02:00:10,960
<font color="#00ffff">He's heading out</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on the north leg.</font>

1130
02:00:10,960 --> 02:00:15,200
<font color="#00ffff">I guess he'll take</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a long, slow descent.</font>

1131
02:00:15,200 --> 02:00:20,720
<font color="#00ffff">Couldn't ask for a better night.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Possibilities unlimited.</font>

1132
02:00:20,720 --> 02:00:24,680
<font color="#00ffff">Ah, there he goes,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">starting his turn.</font>

1133
02:00:24,680 --> 02:00:27,320
<font color="#00ffff">We'd better get moving.</font>

1134
02:00:29,000 --> 02:00:31,880
<font color="#00ffff">He'll land in a few minutes.</font>

1135
02:00:35,240 --> 02:00:37,800
<font color="#00ff00">Come along, Eve. </font><font color="#ffffff">All right.</font>

1136
02:00:37,800 --> 02:00:43,040
<font color="#ffffff">Oh! I think I left my earrings</font>
<font color="#ffffff">upstairs. I'll be right down.</font>

1137
02:00:55,600 --> 02:01:00,600
<font color="#ffff00">Darling. Come, out by the window.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Roger, you'll RUIN everything.</font>

1138
02:01:00,600 --> 02:01:04,040
<font color="#ffff00">They know about the fake shooting.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font>

1139
02:01:04,040 --> 02:01:11,200
<font color="#ffff00">And that figure is full</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of microfilm. </font><font color="#ffffff">THAT'S how</font>
<font color="#ffffff">he's been getting it.</font>

1140
02:01:11,200 --> 02:01:14,520
<font color="#00ffff">Miss Kendall!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Don't get on that plane.</font>

1141
02:01:21,720 --> 02:01:27,640
<font color="#00ff00">You and your husband will be over</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Canadian border by tomorrow.</font>

1142
02:01:27,640 --> 02:01:30,800
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you very much, sir.</font>

1143
02:01:30,800 --> 02:01:33,080
<font color="#ffffff">God bless you.</font>

1144
02:01:47,920 --> 02:01:50,880
<font color="#ffffff">I'll wait, sir.</font>

1145
02:01:50,880 --> 02:01:53,400
<font color="#ffffff">Take care.</font>

1146
02:01:53,400 --> 02:01:56,200
<font color="#ffffff">Thanks very much.</font>

1147
02:01:56,200 --> 02:01:59,680
<font color="#ffffff">PLANE CAN BE HEARD OVERHEAD</font>

1148
02:02:04,200 --> 02:02:06,240
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR CLOSES</font>

1149
02:02:33,240 --> 02:02:35,680
<font color="#ffffff">Stay where you are.</font>

1150
02:02:46,400 --> 02:02:48,480
<font color="#ffffff">Sit down.</font>

1151
02:02:51,000 --> 02:02:55,800
<font color="#ffffff">As soon as the plane leaves,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mr Leonard will be back.</font>

1152
02:02:55,800 --> 02:02:58,960
<font color="#ffffff">PLANE ABOUT TO LAND</font>

1153
02:03:14,760 --> 02:03:18,520
<font color="#ffffff">PLANE TAXIS UP RUNWAY</font>

1154
02:03:22,320 --> 02:03:24,280
<font color="#00ff00">What is it?</font>

1155
02:03:24,280 --> 02:03:28,720
<font color="#ffffff">I was wondering about my earrings.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">They'll turn up.</font>

1156
02:03:33,240 --> 02:03:36,360
<font color="#00ff00">Say goodbye to my sister for me.</font>

1157
02:03:36,360 --> 02:03:39,960
<font color="#00ff00">Thank her for playing Mrs Townsend.</font>

1158
02:03:39,960 --> 02:03:42,560
<font color="#00ff00">Thank your knife-throwing friend.</font>

1159
02:03:42,560 --> 02:03:45,960
<font color="#00ff00">That's about all, Leonard.</font>

1160
02:03:49,400 --> 02:03:51,360
<font color="#ffffff">< GUNSHOTS</font>

1161
02:03:59,080 --> 02:04:01,560
<font color="#00ff00">Get that figure back from her.</font>

1162
02:04:07,400 --> 02:04:12,480
<font color="#ffff00">The housekeeper had me pinned down</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with that silly gun of yours -</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I only just realised.</font>

1163
02:04:12,480 --> 02:04:14,240
<font color="#ffff00">You've got the pumpkin. </font><font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

1164
02:04:51,240 --> 02:04:53,760
<font color="#ffff00">We're on top of the monument.</font>

1165
02:05:11,120 --> 02:05:13,920
<font color="#ffffff">What will we do? </font><font color="#ffff00">Climb down.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">We can't!</font>

1166
02:05:13,920 --> 02:05:16,400
<font color="#ffff00">Here they come. We have no choice.</font>

1167
02:06:04,400 --> 02:06:09,880
<font color="#ffff00">If we ever get out of this alive,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">we'll go to New York on the train.</font>

1168
02:06:09,880 --> 02:06:15,600
<font color="#ffffff">Is that a proposition?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It's a proposal, sweetie.</font>

1169
02:06:15,600 --> 02:06:19,440
<font color="#ffffff">What happened to the first</font>
<font color="#ffffff">two marriages?</font>

1170
02:06:19,440 --> 02:06:22,440
<font color="#ffff00">My wives divorced me. </font><font color="#ffffff">Why?</font>

1171
02:06:22,440 --> 02:06:25,840
<font color="#ffff00">They said I led too dull a life.</font>

1172
02:06:35,120 --> 02:06:37,520
<font color="#ffff00">Are you all right?</font>

1173
02:06:47,400 --> 02:06:51,040
<font color="#ffff00">OK. Come on. Come on, get up.</font>

1174
02:06:53,160 --> 02:06:55,200
<font color="#ffff00">Come on.</font>

1175
02:08:38,360 --> 02:08:39,440
<font color="#ffffff">Aaaah!</font>

1176
02:08:58,800 --> 02:08:59,880
<font color="#ffffff">Aaah! ></font>

1177
02:09:32,120 --> 02:09:34,160
<font color="#ffff00">Help.</font>

1178
02:09:34,160 --> 02:09:36,280
<font color="#ffff00">Help me.</font>

1179
02:09:54,440 --> 02:09:56,400
<font color="#ffffff">GUNSHOT</font>

1180
02:10:04,920 --> 02:10:09,440
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you, sergeant.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">That wasn't very sporting.</font>

1181
02:10:09,440 --> 02:10:13,120
<font color="#ffff00">Reach. Now. </font><font color="#ffffff">I'm...trying.</font>

1182
02:10:13,120 --> 02:10:16,920
<font color="#ffff00">I've got you. </font><font color="#ffffff">I can't make it...</font>

1183
02:10:16,920 --> 02:10:19,640
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, you CAN. Come on. </font><font color="#ffffff">Liar...</font>

1184
02:10:19,640 --> 02:10:21,720
<font color="#ffff00">Come along, Mrs Thornhill.</font>

1185
02:10:25,960 --> 02:10:30,280
<font color="#ffffff">This is silly. </font><font color="#ffff00">I know,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but I'm sentimental.</font>

